Green Arrow (000 - 033) (2011 - Ongoing) (Digital) (Empire) 


The New 52 relaunch of Green Arrow starring a younger, somewhat re-imagined Oliver Queen. The book was first written by previous Green Arrow writer J.T. Krul, with art by Dan Jurgens and George Perez, who were then followed by writer Ann Nocenti and artists Harvey Tolibao and Freddie E. Williams II.
